data.description: Looking for your next Florida Home and need a great interest rate? Well this Beautiful 2-Story Home has an assumable mortgage at 3.25% interest! Located within the highly sought-after Resort-Style Savanna at Lakewood Ranch Community, this Spacious 4-Bedroom, 3.5 Bathroom Home with an Office and Bonus/Game Room has plenty of space to entertain and can fit all of your needs. When you step inside, you will instantly fall in love and be blown away by the high 10-feet ceilings and oversized doors. The Gourmet eat-in Kitchen includes lots of granite counter space with a lot of room to cook amazing meals. The hard wood cabinets have plenty of space to store your best china. Adjacent to the Kitchen, you will find the Dining Room, Great Room and Laundry Room. The oversized first floor Master Bedroom includes an En Suite with a large shower and soaking tub, as well as a Walk-In Closet. What more can you ask for? The upstairs Bonus/Game Room with a closet is a great place to have fun or relax. This Beautiful Home has large bedrooms with plenty of storage space. The screened-in lanai is a perfect place to relax with a cup of coffee in the morning or a glass of wine at night. The large backyard has enough space to add a pool and outdoor kitchen. It is conveniently located close to great schools, lots of shopping and grocery store options, awesome restaurants, fun entertainment and the beautiful Gulf-Coast beaches.     Call today to schedule a tour!
